Module kivakit.resource

Package com.telenav.kivakit.resource.resources

package com.telenav.kivakit.resource.resources
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    InputResource
    An InputStream stream wrapper that allows *one-time* reading of an input stream as a ReadableResource.
    NullResource
    A writable resource that accepts anything you write and destroys it, so when you read there is nothing to be seen.
    OutputResource
    An OutputStream stream wrapper that turns the output stream into a WritableResource.
    PackageResource
    A readable Resource in a package, as specified by PackagePath or ModuleResource (which has a ModuleReference and URI), and a name.
    PackageResource.Resolver
    Resolves ResourceIdentifiers of the form "classpath:/a/b/resource.txt" into Resources by creating a PackageResource for the identifier.
    ResourceSection
    A portion of a resource from one offset into the resource to another.
    StringOutputResource
    A ReadableResource formed from a string passed to the constructor StringOutputResource().
    StringResource
    A ReadableResource formed from a string passed to the constructor StringResource(String).
